fields.name: Beginning Django E-Commerce
fields.description: Learn how to build powerful e-commerce websites with Django, the most popular Python web framework.

fields.name: Test-Driven JavaScript Development
fields.description: Learn how to write unit test covered JavaScript code for your projects using JsTestRunner, a Google open source test runner.

fields.name: MySQL High Availability
fields.description: Learn the ins and outs of setting up MySQL replication for your projects. An excellent resource written by three developers who helped develop the replication features for MySQL.

fields.name: Metaprogramming Ruby
fields.description: A book that covers some more advanced features of the Ruby programming language. A great resource to show seasoned programmers just how deep the rabbit hole goes.

fields.name: Building the Realtime User Experience
fields.description: Learn how to build real-time user experiences on your websites using a Python server called Tornado. You'll build a chat box in your site, work with the Twitter API, and look at how to integrate SMS into your sites.
